title: How do I enter and exit safe mode?
answer:
When your phone is powering on, touch and hold the menu key until the phone vibrates to enter safe mode. After the phone is powered on, Save mode is displayed in the lower left corner. 

 ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=113102) ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=113103)

 To exit safe mode, restart your phone.
